    "name": "Their Navy Is Their Doom",
    "steam_appid": 3186930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Their Navy is Their Doom is a chilling horror game that puts you in command of an advanced combat submarine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive submarine control through tactile cranks, levers, and buttons.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate treacherous waters, launching torpedoes to obliterate enemy vessels while fighting for survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the terrifying secrets lurking in the ocean's darkest depths .</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A concise, intense experience designed to be completed in <strong>under 50 minutes.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186930/extras/8048cc540b00864de8ea2622e46f289a.poster.avif?t=1729375023\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186930/extras/8048cc540b00864de8ea2622e46f289a.webm?t=1729375023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186930/extras/8048cc540b00864de8ea2622e46f289a.mp4?t=1729375023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >THE GAMEPLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Plunge into the abyss beyond the Mariana Trench, tasked with eradicating the last vestiges of the Republic's forces. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over five harrowing days, you'll navigate using sonar and tactical displays, engaging enemy ships in deadly underwater combat. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Due to the experimental nature of your vessel and limited resources, you'll enter cryosleep during descents to uncharted depths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186930/extras/a65e3496be78b4426a5fc18c35baf4d6.poster.avif?t=1729375023\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186930/extras/a65e3496be78b4426a5fc18c35baf4d6.webm?t=1729375023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186930/extras/a65e3496be78b4426a5fc18c35baf4d6.mp4?t=1729375023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >THE STORY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As Commander Kenji Nagai of the Federation, you stand at the precipice of history. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Federation has triumphed in the land war, driving the Republic's leadership to flee with their remaining naval forces through a covert passage drilled deep beneath the Mariana Trench. You helm one of the few cutting-edge submarines dispatched to deliver the final blow. To withstand the crushing pressure of extreme depths, you must rely on cryosleep as your vessel auto-navigates the perilous descent.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The fate of the world rests in your hands, Commander Nagai.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186930/extras/b55248de804c96f0377bb9d707fcb8af.poster.avif?t=1729375023\" width=600 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186930/extras/b55248de804c96f0377bb9d707fcb8af.webm?t=1729375023\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186930/extras/b55248de804c96f0377bb9d707fcb8af.mp4?t=1729375023\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
